body:
Wache Gordon Wache Who goes by the Artistic name Wache G. Is a Multi-talented Cameroon Gospel Artist, stage Performer, singer, Songwriter, Instrumentalist, and recording Artist. 

 He was Born on the 28th Of March 1996 in Nkambe. He is originally from Fonfuka(Bum) in the northwest region of Cameroon. He was born to the family of Rev & Past Mrs. Wache Emmanuel .he is the 3rd Child of a family of 6.


 In his Teenage years Gordon Became a born Again Christian Baptized on the 4th of April 2010 .he became a church instrumentalist at a tender age at Berean Baptist church Kumba Cameroon.


Wache G Discovered His singing Potential in 2017 When he served as a music Tutor and teacher at Covenant Baptist Church.
 

 Gordon Obtained his Ordinary and advance level certificate at B.H.S NDOP and later Proceeded to the university in 2015 Were he studied Software Engineering at Landmark university College (HND). And later moved to the university of Buea Were he obtained a Degree.


 Wache G is a member of Berean Baptist Church Kumba as Home Church .and a member of Christland Ministries Buea were he serves As Church administrator. 
 Wache G is Currently Signed to Worship Nation Music label.



<!--EndFragment-->
